 = Pushwoosh.configure.getHWID()","","        \/\/ Sync with various analytics platforms","        Analytics.identify(userId)","        Crashlytics.setUserID(userId)","        MixpanelInstance.identify(distinctId: userId)","","        \/\/ Log device mapping for debugging","        Logger.debug(\"User identity: userId=\\(userId), hwid=\\(hwid)\")","    }","","    func trackEventWithUserContext(_ event: String, properties: [String: Any]) {","        var enrichedProperties = properties","        enrichedProperties[\"pushwoosh_user_id\"] = Pushwoosh.configure.getUserId()","        enrichedProperties[\"pushwoosh_hwid\"] = Pushwoosh.configure.getHWID()","","        Analytics.track(event, properties: enrichedProperties)","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Retrieves the current user identifier."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/getuserid"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"type":"topic","title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/getUserId":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"getUserId","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/getUserId","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/getuserid","title":"getUserId","abstract":[{"text":"Retrieves the current user identifier.","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"getUserId"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwo